comments.body:
@givensuman please squash (fixup) the commits into one as mentioned in https://github.com/containers/podman/pull/27420#pullrequestreview-3412415011, we like a proper git history with useful commit messages.
And as @mheon mentioned you will need to rebase as well on main to make the CI happy.

If you don't know how to squash and rebase I am happy to do it or give you instructions on how to.
